latestPosts.caption:
woke up one day to realise @iakpataudi and @khushikapoor were shooting on campus and not only did I get to watch, but somehow got a chance to do a background role 🎬

mad fun being on set, going for costumes, hair/makeup and seeing the daily campus being turned into a dharma high school was wild⭐️

But yeah being a tiny tiny lil part of something so exciting and seeing how much goes into a film as a bollywood junkie was definitely insane. Go watch #nadaaniyan if you haven’t already! 📚

#bollywood #ibrahimalikhan #khushikapoor #bollywoodoncampus #dharma #bts #collegelife
